name: Steve Russell Opening A Gate To Hell With The PDP-1 Minicomputer
description: © John David Pressman. A satirical portrayal of AI pioneer Stephen Russell pondering an opened gate to hell (here depicted as a kind of black hole or orb) made in response to panicked claims that deep learning programs achieve their results not through statistics, but computer scientists using Satanic rituals which bind demons to do their will.; 2021 CLIP Guided-Conditioned Diffusion 1024x1024
